{"tid":1124214,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我身為獌迷，今日返工頭耷耷","createTime":"2019-04-25T01:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T13:56:55.000Z","uid":174953,"like":31,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8e4815cc32971d4c90968953ce6604aac091bab4","tid":1124214,"uid":174953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:54:03.000Z","msg":"是咁的，捱夜睇完獌主場打毗輸波既我，心情已經低落到一個點，之後仲要死死氣咁返份廢工，返到office又準備要比班鏝車迷恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩既係我有個阿迷同事，有佢陪我一齊比人笑都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我就連平時會去麥記食個豬柳強既心情都無，頭耷耷咁死返去公司。<br />\n<br />\n去到公司樓下，準備搭𨋢上去既我，見到有條友匿埋左係架𨋢既一角，頭又未洗，恤衫又未攝好，仲係度喊緊，嚇到其他OL都唔敢企佢身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我心諗睇黎佢都係捱夜睇完愛隊輸波，於是我就走埋去搭佢膊頭同佢講：巴打，下季踢歐霸姐，我地獌聯又唔係未試過，唔洗咁灰既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知佢突然大叫，我猁迷黎嫁，屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n我當堂由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之後我聽到身邊既OL都恥笑緊佢。<br />\n<br />\n一開𨋢，條友就衝咗出去指住我地講，I WILL BE BACK！"},{"pid":"9193ea89747f36f190009b67b5f3d3ed825211e9","tid":1124214,"uid":4586,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:56:01.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"184c00aa46c466603d5b3ce037c480d2c6ee3f85","tid":1124214,"uid":174953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9193ea89747f36f190009b67b5f3d3ed825211e9","tid":1124214,"uid":4586,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:56:01.000Z","msg":"55"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58389f27651f4911be1350ad9e1578ee1b285f95","tid":1124214,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:59:22.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"9763b686c581bfd8103e